4. Mathematical Framework

CCE uses a state triple:

s = (v, τ, r)

Where:

v = literal vector

τ = relational tension vector

r = curvature response coefficient


4.1 Curvature Operator (C)

C(s) = s × (1 + ε)

ε typically 1%–3%.

4.2 Tension Mapping (T)

τ = ∇ relational_field

4.3 Resonance Propagation (Φ)

Φ(s_i, s_j) = exp( - |τ_i - τ_j| / r )

4.4 Insight Condition

Σ Φ ≥ κ


